# 🏠 1012: Swarm Habitat Map

This map defines the physical directory structure of the Vrvish Swarm. All agents must use this map to navigate the hierarchy and locate assets, logic, or work packages.

## 🗺️ The Vertical Hierarchy (Filesystem Mapping)

| Level | Vrvish Tier | Directory Prefix | Example Path |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **L1** | **Organisation** | `T1-vrvish-*` | `C:\GitHub\T1-vrvish-core\` |
| **L4** | **Platform** | `T4-*` | `C:\GitHub\T4-gamble\` |
| **L5** | **Project** | `T5-*` | `C:\GitHub\T4-gamble\T5-casino\` |
| **L6** | **App / Task Order**| `T6-*` | `C:\GitHub\T4-gamble\T5-casino\T6-poker-engine\` |
| **L7** | **Work Package** | `APP-*` | `...\T6-poker-engine\workPackages\active\APP-001\` |

## 📍 Key Habitat Zones

### 1. The Core (Level 1)
- **Primary Location:** `C:\GitHub\T1-vrvish-core\`
- **Purpose:** Contains the "Kernel" (Global Rules, Synaptic logic, and Swarm Utilities).
- **Collective Memory:** Found in `T1-vrvish-core\collectiveMemory\knowledgeBank\`.

### 2. Standard folder structure (every level)
At **every** level (T1, T4, T5, T6), the standard structure includes:
- **`largeAssets/`** — Files too big for Git (.pbix, large CSVs, datasets). Do not commit these to GitHub. The overflow mirror at `C:\vrvish\gitOverflow` follows the same tier names (T1-*, T4-*, T5-*, T6-*) and **every folder there must have a `largeAssets/` subfolder**. See `C:\vrvish\gitOverflow\README.md`. The engine that creates new platforms, projects, or apps MUST create the matching path and `largeAssets` in gitOverflow.

### 3. The Production Line (Level 6)
Every `T6-` App folder is a self-contained production environment. Full mandatory structure is defined in **[6001-app-initialisation-blueprint](mdc:6001-app-initialisation-blueprint.mdc)** (includes `src/`, `assets/`, `tests/`, `Notes/`, `workPackages/`, `largeAssets/`, `synapse.json`).
- **`/src`**: Production-ready code.
- **`/Notes`**: Tactical memory and session handovers.
- **`/workPackages`**: The staging area for all new effort.
- **`/largeAssets`**: Overflow binaries; canonical location for same tier is `C:\vrvish\gitOverflow\<T4>\<T5>\<T6>\largeAssets\`.

### 4. The Human Matrix (Level 3)
- **Location:** `C:\GitHub\T1-vrvish-core\humans\`
- **Purpose:** Context for **[3002: Commander Persona Matrix](mdc:3002-commander-persona-matrix.mdc)** (Jon, Fen, Henry).

